2.2 Relationships with industry and other conflicts of interest
It is ESC policy to sponsor position papers and Guidelines without commercial support, and all members volunteered their time. Thus, all members of the writing group, as well as the reviewers, have disclosed any potential conflicts of interest in detail. The details of these declarations will be posted on the ESC website upon publication of these Guidelines.

